Rapid Spanning Tree Configuration (RSTP)
!
spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst
spanning-tree portfast default
spanning-tree bpduguard default
!
Optional Root Bridge Configuration (Core Switch Only)
spanning-tree vlan 1-4094 priority 4096 (range is only vlans on router)
!
Optional Secondary Root (Distribution Layer)
spanning-tree vlan 1-4094 priority 8192  (range is only vlans on router)
